('20081022100445', '20080919070258', '20080919070002', 'Garmin Nuvi 710i', NULL, NULL, '20081022100445-nuvi_710ix.jpg', 0, 0, '4700000', NULL, NULL, 'Arrive stress-free with n&uuml;vi 710, a GPS navigator and personal travel assistant. Sold exclusively in Europe, n&uuml;vi 710 comes with preloaded map data for a specific region or country on the continent and includes advanced navigation features, a widescreen display, preloaded maps, an FM transmitter, hands-free calling and more. Like the rest of the wide n&uuml;vi 700-series, its premium navigation capabilities, like route planning and an emergency locator, give you peace of mind on the go.<br />See More<br /><br />With n&uuml;vi 710&#39;s widescreen display, you&#39;ll always get the big picture. View map detail, driving directions, photos and more in bright, brilliant color. Its sunlight-readable, 4.3-inch display is easy to read &mdash; from any direction.<br />Navigate With Ease<br /><br />n&uuml;vi 710 comes ready to go right out of the box with preloaded City Navigator&reg; NT street maps and millions of points of interest (POIs) such as hotels, restaurants, fuel stations, ATMs and more. Simply touch the color screen to enter a destination, and n&uuml;vi takes you there with 2-D or 3-D maps and turn-by-turn voice directions. In addition, n&uuml;vi 710 accepts custom points of interest, such as school zones and safety cameras and lets you set proximity alerts to warn you of upcoming POIs. Some versions even include a preloaded safety camera database.<br />Where Am I?<br /><br />Keep track of yourself and your car with n&uuml;vi 710. Just tap "Where Am I?" to find the closest hospitals, police stations, fuel stations, nearest address and intersection. Also see your exact latitude and longitude coordinates. n&uuml;vi 710 even remembers where you parked. It automatically marks your position when you remove it from the windshield mount, so you can navigate with n&uuml;vi on foot and find your way back to your vehicle. Perfect for unfamiliar spots and crowded lots such as amusement parks, stadiums and malls.<br />Plan Ahead<br /><br />n&uuml;vi 710 includes advanced navigational features to take the worry out of traveling. With route planning you can save 10 routes, specify via points and preview simulated turns on the 710&#39;s wide screen. In addition, n&uuml;vi 710 automatically sorts multiple destinations to provide an efficient route for errands, deliveries or sales calls. It also displays speed limits for highways and Interstates. A trip log provides an electronic bread crumb trail of up to 10,000 points, so you can see where you&#39;ve been on the map.<br />Make Hands-free Calls<br /><br />Talk about worry-free driving. n&uuml;vi 710 integrates Bluetooth&reg; wireless technology with a built-in microphone and speaker for hands-free calling. Just pair it with your compatible Bluetooth phone and talk hands-free through the 710 while staying focused on the road. Simply dial numbers with n&uuml;vi&#39;s touchscreen keypad to make a call. To answer calls, just tap the screen and speak directly into its built-in microphone.<br />Avoid Traffic Tie-ups<br /><br />Steer clear of traffic with n&uuml;vi 710&#39;s integrated FM TMC traffic receiver. Receive alerts about traffic delays and road construction that lie ahead on your route. Next, simply touch n&uuml;vi&#39;s screen to view traffic details or detour around the problem area.<br />Take It With You<br /><br />n&uuml;vi 710&#39;s high-sensitivity internal (non flip-up) antenna gives it a sleeker, thinner design than the n&uuml;vi 600-series, making it easy to slip in your pocket or purse. Its rechargeable lithium-ion battery makes it convenient for navigation by car or on foot.<br />Go Beyond Navigation<br /><br />Navigation is just the beginning. n&uuml;vi 710 includes many &ldquo;must have&rdquo; entertainment and travel tools including MP3 player, audio book player (subscription to Audible.com required), JPEG picture viewer, currency converters and more. With n&uuml;vi 710&#39;s wireless FM transmitter&sup1; you can hear audio, including voice prompts, MP3s and audio books, through your vehicle&#39;s stereo. It&#39;s also compatible with optional FM traffic alerts or optional MSN&reg; Direct content. The 710 features Garmin Lock&trade;, an anti-theft feature, and is compatible with our free Garmin Garage where you can download custom vehicles that show your location on the map. Optional software on plug-and-play SD cards for language translation, detailed travel guide and savings program allow you to customize n&uuml;vi for your travel needs.', '<table id="playlist" border="0" cellspacing="0">\r <tbody>\r <tr class="title">\r <td colspan="2">\r <h3>Physical &amp; Performance:</h3>\r </td>\r </tr>\r <tr class="odd">\r <td>Unit dimensions, WxHxD:</td>\r <td>4.8"W x 3.0"H x .8"D (12.2 x 7.6 x 2.0 cm)</td>\r </tr>\r <tr class="even">\r <td>Display size, WxH:</td>\r <td>3.81"W x 2.25"H (9.7 x 5.7 cm); 4.3" diag (10.9 cm)</td>\r </tr>\r <tr class="odd">\r <td>Display resolution, WxH:</td>\r <td>480 x 272 pixels</td>\r </tr>\r <tr class="even">\r <td>Display type:</td>\r <td>WQVGA color TFT with white backlight</td>\r </tr>\r <tr class="odd">\r <td>Weight:</td>\r <td>6.2 ounces (176 g)</td>\r </tr>\r <tr class="even">\r <td>Battery:</td>\r <td>rechargeable lithium-ion</td>\r </tr>\r <tr class="odd">\r <td>Battery life:</td>\r <td>up to 5 hours</td>\r </tr>\r <tr class="even">\r <td>Waterproof:</td>\r <td>no</td>\r </tr>\r <tr class="odd">\r <td>High-sensitivity receiver:</td>\r <td>yes</td>\r </tr>\r <tr class="even">\r <td>RoHS version available:</td>\r <td>yes</td>\r </tr>\r </tbody>\r </table>\r <table id="playlist" border="0" cellspacing="0">\r <tbody>\r <tr class="title">\r <td colspan="2">\r <h3>Maps &amp; Memory:</h3>\r </td>\r </tr>\r <tr class="odd">\r <td>Basemap:</td>\r <td>yes</td>\r </tr>\r <tr class="even">\r <td>Preloaded maps:</td>\r <td>yes (regional)</td>\r </tr>\r <tr