('20081115153017', '20080919070322', '20081103201619', 'M-3', NULL, '<span class="normal"> premium quality ergonomically designed precision compass for accurate and convenient direction taking.</span> <br /><br /><strong><span class="header">Professional Compasses for Demanding Navigators </span></strong><br /><br /><span class="normal">The two models, which make up the M-Series (M-2, M-3), represent durable, reliable, high quality navigational aids, which perform flawlessly in even the most demanding of conditions. Both models feature a large liquid filled capsule and adjustable declination correction scale. Another convenient feature of the models in this series is the serrated bezel ring, which is easy to turn even in cold conditions while wearing gloves. Due to their easy-to-read luminous markings and magnifying lenses, the compasses of the M-Series are also ideally suited to navigating in conditions of poor visibility.</span> <br /><br /><span class="ode"><strong>Product Features</strong><br /><br /></span> <span class="normal">\r <li>Two Zone System</li>\r <li>also available with global needle</li>\r <li>serrated bezel ring</li>\r <li>jewel bearing</li>\r <li> adjustable declination correction scale</li>\r <li> base plate with anti-slip rubber pads and rounded edges </li>\r <li>magnifying lens</li>\r <li>luminous markings </li>\r <li>marking holes for drawing control points </li>\r <li>size: 60 x 125 mm /2.4" x 4.9"</li>\r <li>weight: 44 g / 1.6 oz</li>\r </span>', '20081115153017-m3_150x.jpg', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('20081115155515', '20080919070322', '20081103201619', 'Suunto X9', NULL, '<span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Suunto X9 has everything you need for a successful journey. Packed with a GPS, compass, chronograph, altimeter, and barometer it will take you through even the toughest situations.<br /><br />Suunto X9 is the ultimate tool for any cross sports enthusiast who want to plan their journey carefully, wish to know exactly where they are at all times and have a high regard for safety. <br /><br />Suunto X9 gives you all the information on your performance you need to improve your training. It also records and stores data for later analysis. You can view, compare, and analyze your performance with specially designed PC software. <br /><br />The sophisticated features of the wristop computer, combined with the PC software developed to give more graphical representation of your performance, and our Internet Community, where you can share information with other like-minded people from around the world, make Suunto X9 the device of choice for every serious adventurer and athlete.<br /><br />Features:&nbsp; <br /><br /></span>\r <ul>\r <li><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Altimeter: altitude, vertical speed, altitude alrem, thermometer </span></li>\r <li><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Barometer: Sea level pressure, absolute pressure, weather trend graph, temperature, weather alarm </span></li>\r <li><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">3D Compass: Bearing, graphic compass rose, bearing tracking </span></li>\r <li><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">GPS: Resolution 1m / 3ft, 12 channels </span></li>\r <li><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Watch: Calendar, 3 alarms with date option, dual time, stopwatch </span></li>\r <li><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Menu-based user interface familiar from mobile phones </span></li>\r <li><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Rechargeable battery </span></li>\r <li><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Water resistant to 10 bar </span></li>\r <li><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">PC interface software + cable </span></li>\r <li><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;">Full access to SuuntoSports.com </span></li>\r </ul>', '20081115155515-9_150150x.gif', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('20081115161304', '20080919070322', '20081103201619', 'Suunto X9i', '<strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: #000000;">Suunto X9i, the World&#39;s Smallest Outdoor Wristop Computer with GPS</span></span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><br /></span>', NULL, '20081117141142-9i_150150x.gif', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: #000000;">Suunto X9i, the world&#39;s smallest outdoor wristop computer with GPS, is now compatible with several digital mapping services across the world. The upgraded Suunto X9i features a new USB charger and PC connector so outdoor enthusiasts can now charge their device through a PC. The new Suunto X9i will be available in two color choices: black and tan. <br /><br />Utilizing digital mapping software, users are not only able to plan their routes on a digital map, but can also print their own customized maps and download routes from the software directly onto the Suunto X9i. In this way, route planning and waypoint programming is fast, accurate and simple. <br /><br />When navigating on a pre-planned route, the Suunto X9i shows the direction and remaining distance to the next waypoint and calculates the estimated time of arrival. During activities, the Suunto X9i shows the current speed and distance traveled using GPS functions. The &#39;Find home&#39; setting guides the way back to the start point or marked &#39;Home&#39; position whilst the &#39;Track back&#39; function guides the user back along any recorded route. <br /><br />The Suunto X9i is the world&#39;s smallest and lightest wrist-mounted GPS unit. In addition, it incorporates an altimeter, barometer, digital compass, thermometer, and an extensive memory, as well as the usual time/stopwatch functions. Combining all of these functions into a sleek, sporty wristop computer not only enhances safety, but also adds a whole new dimension to the outdoor experience.<br /><br />The Suunto X9i will be available in fall 2005. <br /><br />Suunto is the leading manufacturer of sports instruments for a variety of sports, including training, golf, skiing, hiking, diving and sailing. The company&#39;s focus is on sports activities where advanced measurement technology and data processing can generate significant performance benefits for active people. Suunto, headquartered in Vantaa, Finland, is a wholly owned subsidiary of the Helsinki-based Amer Sports Corporation.</span></span>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('20081115164122', '20080919070322', '20081103201619', 'MB-6', NULL, '<span class="normal">A Feature-Packed compass in a Handy Matchbox Style Case.</span> <br /><br /><span class="normal">The Suunto MB-6 is a combination of a hand bearing and base plate compass in a highly resistant Noryl&acute;s matchbox style case and is ideal for marine use. Though small and compact, the MB-6 boasts a host of invaluable features.</span> <br /><br /><span class="ode"><strong>Product Features :</strong><br /><br /></span> <span class="normal">\r <li> Two Zone System</li>\r <li> matchbox style</li>\r <li> highly resistant case</li>\r <li> jewel bearing</li>\r <li> adjustable declination correction scale</li>\r <li> luminous needle</li>\r <li> clinometer</li>\r </span>', '20081115164122-mb-6_150x.jpg', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('20081115164618', '20080919070322', '20081103201619', 'Comet', NULL, '<span class="normal">A premium quality micro compass, with thermometer and key ring, for town or country navigation.</span> <br /><br /><strong><span class="header">Premium Quality Outdoor Accessories</span></strong><br /><br /><span class="normal">The Suunto Micro Compass series comprises two models, Clipper and Comet, which feature a liquid filled capsule and rotating dial. An invaluable navigational tool in town or country, the compass can be clipped to a watch band or bag strap, or used as a key ring to ensure that the compass is always with you when you need it. A Suunto Micro Compass, customized with a company logo, makes an ideal and practical business gift.</span> <br /><br /><strong><span class="ode">Product Features<br /><br /></span></strong> <span class="normal">\r <li>Two Zone System (available for northern hemisphere only)</li>\r <li> thermometer</li>\r <li>jewel bearing</li>\r <li>wind chill chart</li>\r <li> key ring</li>\r <li>size: 26 x 78 mm / 1" x 3.1"</li>\r </span>', '20081115164618-comet_150x.jpg', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
