('20081210180445', '20081020145007', '20081210181519', 'Leica DISTO D2', NULL, '<strong><span class="teaser">Precise measurements - fast and easy - fits into every pocket</span></strong> <br /><br />The compact and handy base model was specifically designed for indoor applications. Shortcut keys for addition, subtraction, area and volume calculation make measuring fast and very reliable. As with all Leica laser distance meters, the laser dot is clearly visible. You can always see your targeting point even if the target object is in a hard to access areas.  <br /><br /><span class="text"><strong>Small and handy</strong></span> <br /><br /><span class="text">it is easy to hold due to its compact but ergonomical size - and fits into every pocket.</span> <br /><br /><span class="text"><strong>Easiest to use</strong></span> <br /><br /><span class="text">it could not be any easier - point the laser beam at the target, press the DIST-key and read the measured value.</span> <br /><br /><span class="text"><strong>Illuminated display</strong></span> <br /><br /><span class="text">makes measured values easy to read, even in the dark.</span>', '20081210180445-Disto-A2x.jpg', 0, 0, '2700000', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<table border="0" width="468">\r <tbody>\r <tr>\r <td style="width: 90px;"><br /></td>\r <td></td>\r </tr>\r </tbody>\r </table>\r <table style="border-collapse: collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" width="468" bordercolor="#cccccc">\r <tbody>\r <tr bgcolor="#e6e6e6">\r <th>Features</th> <th>Your advantages</th>\r </tr>\r <tr>\r <td><span class="headline">Measuring range of 0.05 til 60m  <br /> typ. accuracy &plusmn; 1.5mm</span></td>\r <td><span class="headline"><span class="headline">Precise, fast and reliable indoor measurements</span></span></td>\r </tr>\r <tr>\r <td><span class="headline">Handy size</span></td>\r <td><span class="headline"><span class="headline">Fits any pocket</span></span></td>\r </tr>\r <tr>\r <td><span class="headline"> Direct keys</span></td>\r <td><span class="headline"> Easy to use</span></td>\r </tr>\r <tr>\r <td><span class="headline"> <span class="headline">Illuminated display</span></span></td>\r <td><span class="headline"> See the values also in the dark</span></td>\r </tr>\r <tr>\r <td>Ergonomic</td>\r <td>The instrument is easy to hold, all keys <br /> are ergonomically arranged</td>\r </tr>\r <tr>\r <td>Stake-out function</td>\r <td>Stakes out equal (constant) distances.<br /> The display shows the preset distance <br /> and its multiples. A beep is sounded <br /> whenever such a distance point is reached.</td>\r </tr>\r </tbody>\r </table>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('20081210184135', '20081020145007', '20081210181519', 'Leica Disto D3', NULL, NULL, '20081210184135-Leica-Disto-A3x.gif', 0, 0, '4650000', NULL, NULL, 'Mengukur dimudahkan &ndash; dalam ukuran yang kecil! BARU  <br /><br />Ukuran minimal dan operasi yang sederhana adalah melukiskan karakteristik dari model dasar itu. Kunci singkat untuk penambahan, pengurangan, area, dan volume berarti bahwa mengukur tidak bisa lebih sederhana. Fungsi minimum dan maksimum sekarang juga telah di satukan. Anda bhakan bias mengatakan bahwa unit yang ringkas ini merupakan sebuah kesenagan untuk di gunakan. Dapat dipercaya, sederhana dan &ndash; mulai sekarang &ndash; selalu digenggaman tangan ketika anda memerlukan.\r <ul>\r <li>Dapat dipercaya, sederhana dan &ndash; mulai sekarang &ndash; selalu diterima sampai ditangan ketika anda memerlukan itu. </li>\r <li>Kecil tetapi sempurna </li>\r <li>Cocok dengan sempurna masuk ke dalam saku dan bermanfaat untuk aplikasi masing-masing. </li>\r <li>Sederhana dalam beroperasi </li>\r <li>Menyangkut kunci singkat penambahan, dan pengurangan seperti halnya permukaan dan kalkulasi volume tidak bisa lebih mudah. </li>\r <li>Fungsi spirit-level yang terintegrasi </li>\r <li>Kelurusan horisontal dimudahkan, seperti untuk kotak kontak. </li>\r </ul>\r <br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Fitur-fitur :\r <ul>\r <li>Batas-ukur dari 0.05 sampai 200m (0.16 sampai 650ft); tipe ketelitian &plusmn; 2mm (&plusmn; 0.08in) </li>\r <li>Teknologi cakupan tenaga&trade; </li>\r <li>Ukuran yang kecil </li>\r <li>Kunci singkat </li>\r <li>Pengukuran yang berlanjut </li>\r <li>Fungsi spirit-level yang terintegrasi </li>\r <li>Layar yang diterangi </li>\r <li>Pelapis Tombol Foil keypad </li>\r <li>Mengarahkan bantuan </li>\r </ul>\r <br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Keuntungan-keuntungan anda:\r <ul>\r <li>Pengukuran yang cepat dan akurat </li>\r <li>Ijinkan mengukur dari jauh (perkiraan 100m) tanpa pelat target plate </li>\r <li>Sesuai dengan saku apapun </li>\r <li>Sederhana untuk beroperasi </li>\r <li>Mengukur dari jarak minimum dan yang maksimum, contohnya untuk mengukur sebuah ruang diagonal </li>\r <li>Kelurusan horisontal </li>\r <li>Pembacaan pengukuran kelihatan bahkan di kegelapan </li>\r <li>Tahan terhadap percikan air dan debu; mudah dibersihkan </li>\r <li>Untuk targe berbaris di atas jarak yang lebih jauh dan di ruang terbuka </li>\r </ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('20081210190344', '20081020145007', '20081210181519', 'Leica Disto A5', NULL, 'Jumlah kemampuan maksimum - dengan disain ergonomic BARU  <br /><br />Leica DISTO&trade; A5 menonjol karena dua hal yaitu disain ergonomic dan genggaman karet lunak yang mengijinkan ia/nya untuk duduk baik di tangan. Dengan hasil uniknya, cakupan luas dari fungsi tambahan dan penemuan pandangan yang terintegrasi, Leica DISTO&trade; A5 secara penuh equiped untuk mengerjakan tugas mengukur manapun. Fungsi paling umum menghitung yang sudah jelas cepat dan dengan mudah diakses via kunci singkat yang sesuai.\r <ul>\r <li>Di dalam rumah atau di luar rumah &ndash; Leica DISTO&trade; A5 adalah mitra yang dapat di percaya. </li>\r <li>Disain ergonomic dengan karet lunak genggam </li>\r <li>Serasi dengan sempurna di tangan, dengan genggaman karet lunak untuk memastikan suatu pegangan yang kuat. </li>\r <li>Kesempurnaan yang cukup untuk penggunaan di luar </li>\r <li>Mengintegrasikan hubungan dengan mata viewfinder menyederhanakan pengarahan jarak yang terlalu jauh </li>\r <li>Multi fungsi flip-out hasil akhir </li>\r <li>Sensor built in yang secara otomatis menentukan titik nol yang tepat. </li>\r </ul>\r <br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Liputan:\r <ul>\r <li>Batas-ukur dari 0.05 sampai 200m (0.16 sampai 650ft); tipe ketelitian &plusmn; 2mm (&plusmn; 0.08in) </li>\r <li>Teknologi cakupan tenaga&trade; </li>\r <li>Disain ergonomic dengan karet lunak genggam </li>\r <li>Viewfinder terintegrasi dengan 2x perbesaran </li>\r <li>Kalkulasi ruang </li>\r <li>Pengukuran tinggi-/lebar secara tidak langsung </li>\r <li>Kunci singkat </li>\r </ul>\r <br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Keuntungan-keuntungan anda:\r <ul>\r <li>Pengukuran yang cepat dan yang akurat dari jarak pendek dan jauh </li>\r <li>Ijinkan mengukur dari jauh (perkiraan 100m) tanpa pelat target plate </li>\r <li>Instrumen sesuai di tangan dengan baik </li>\r <li>ideal untuk pengukuran jarak yang lebih panjang </li>\r <li>Hasil yang maksimum dengan usaha yang minimum, tidak ada lagi kalkulasi manual </li>\r <li>Pengukuran dari lokasi yang tidak dapat di masuki </li>\r <li>Operasi ekstra sederhana </li>\r </ul>', '20081210200837-Leica-Disto-A5x.gif', 0, 0, '5000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('20081210201156', '20081020145007', '20081210181519', 'Leica DISTO A6', NULL, '<strong><span class="teaser">Bluetooth&reg; data transfer - for a reliable transfer of measured values</span></strong> <br /><br />The measuring process on the Leica DISTO&trade; A6 isn&rsquo;t over with the display of the results: integrated BLUETOOTH&reg; technology, combined with software designed to let you export measurement readings straight into various programs (e.g. Word&reg; Excel&reg;, AutoCad&reg;) without the use of cables. Take the hard work out of measuring &ndash; it is fun now!  <br /><br /><strong>Wireless transfer via Bluetooth<sup>&reg;</sup></strong> <br /><br /><span class="text">Forget paper and pencil now!</span> <br /><br /><span class="text"><strong>DISTO&trade; transfer</strong></span> <br /><br /><span class="text">Transmits your measured values without wires to your Pocket PC od laptop for further processing - with the program of your choice. The application operates in the background, so will not even notice it running.</span> <br /><br /><span class="text"><strong>Navigation keys</strong></span> <br /><br /><span class="text">control the cursor movement in the software with the Leica DISTO&trade; A6 and leave the pen of your Pocket PC in its holder!</span>', '20081210201156-Leica-Disto-A6x.gif', 0, 0, '7100000', NULL, NULL, '<table style="border-collapse: collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" width="468" bordercolor="#cccccc">\r <tbody>\r <tr bgcolor="#e6e6e6">\r <th>Features</th> <th>Your advantages</th>\r </tr>\r <tr bgcolor="#ffffff">\r <td><span class="headline"><span class="headline">Measuring range of 0.05 up to 200m <br /> (0.16 up to 650ft); typ. accuracy <br /> &plusmn; 1.5 mm (&plusmn; 0.06in)</span></span></td>\r <td><span class="headline"><span class="headline"><span class="headline"><span class="headline">Fast and accurate measurement of <br /> short and long distances</span></span></span></span></td>\r </tr>\r <tr bgcolor="#ffffff">\r <td><span class="headline"> Power Range Technology&trade;</span></td>\r <td>Allows measuring of long distances <br /> (approx. 100m) without target plate</td>\r </tr>\r <tr bgcolor="#ffffff">\r <td><span class="headline"> Integrated viewfinder with <br /> 2x magnification</span></td>\r <td><span class="headline"> Indispensable for measurements outside<br /> esp. at bright sun lights</span></td>\r </tr>\r <tr bgcolor="#ffffff">\r <td><span class="headline"> <span class="headline">Integrierted BLUETOOTH&reg; technology </span></span></td>\r <td><span class="headline"> <span class="headline">Wireless and reliable data transfer to <br /> Pocket PCs and PCs</span></span></td>\r </tr>\r <tr bgcolor="#ffffff">\r <td><span class="headline"> DISTO&trade; transfer</span></td>\r <td><span class="headline"> Free software which sends the measured values<br /> reliably to Excel&reg;, Word&reg;, AutoCad&reg; and many other<br /> softwares.</span></td>\r </tr>\r <tr bgcolor="#ffffff">\r <td>Navigation keys</td>\r <td>Direct control of the cursor movements</td>\r </tr>\r <tr>\r <td>IP54</td>\r <td>Splash and dust proof - important for all professional</td>\r </tr>\r </tbody>\r </table>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('20081210202910', '20081020145007', '20081210181519', 'Leica DISTO A8', NULL, '<strong><span class="teaser">NEW - With digital viewfinder and tilt sensor &ndash; simply perfect!</span></strong> <br /><br />The digital viewfinder and the integrated tilt sensor make the Leica DISTO&trade; A8 an innovation worldwide and open up completely new possibilities. Comfortably find your target with the three-fold digital zoom made even easier with the blended in crosshairs. The brightness of the greyscales display can be manually adjusted; ideal for poorly contrasting targets! The tilt sensor does not only indicate angles, but also real horizontal distances and various indirect height measurements.  <br /><br /><span class="text"><strong>Tilt sensor<sup><br /></sup></strong>Any tilt can be easily measured by just placing the housing on the slope.</span> <br /><br /><span class="text"><strong>Digital viewfinder (3-fold zoom)</strong><br />Essential for far distances and in sunshine.</span> <br /><br /><span class="text"><strong>Indirect height measurements<br /></strong>By using the tilt sensor and the digital viewfinder, heights can be determined in the first measurement even without reflecting the laser beam.</span>', '20081210203605-Leica-Disto-A8x.jpg', 0, 0, '10400000', NULL, NULL, '<table style="border-collapse: collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" width="468" bordercolor="#cccccc">\r <tbody>\r <tr bgcolor="#e6e6e6">\r <th>Features</th> <th>Your advantages</th>\r </tr>\r <tr bgcolor="#ffffff">\r <td><span class="headline"><span class="headline">Measuring range of 0.05 m/0.16 ft up to 200 m/650 ft; typ. accuracy &plusmn; 1.5 mm/ &plusmn; 0.06 in</span></span></td>\r <td><span class="headline"><span class="headline"><span class="headline"><span class="headline">Precise, fast and reliable measurements</span></span></span></span></td>\r </tr>\r <tr bgcolor="#ffffff">\r <td><span class="headline">Power Range Technology&trade;</span></td>\r <td>Measure over long distances (approx. 100 m) without target plate</td>\r </tr>\r <tr bgcolor="#ffffff">\r <td><span class="headline">Digital viewfinder with 3-fold zoom</span></td>\r <td><span class="headline">Easy measurements in sunshine and to far away targets</span></td>\r </tr>\r <tr bgcolor="#ffffff">\r <td><span class="headline"><span class="headline">Tilt sensor</span></span></td>\r <td><span class="headline">Measure tilts by setting the housing on the object</span></td>\r </tr>\r <tr bgcolor="#ffffff">\r <td><span class="headline">Indirect tilt measurements</span></td>\r <td><span class="headline">Height measurements, e.g. without reflecting the laser beam through the tilt sensor</span></td>\r </tr>\r <tr bgcolor="#ffffff">\r <td>Indirect height / distance measurements</td>\r <td><span class="headline">Measure to inaccessible areas &ndash; at the press of the button, more detailed information will be available</span></td>\r </tr>\r <tr>\r <td>Greyscales display</td>\r <td>Best contrast possible; 9 brightness settings available</td>\r </tr>\r <tr>\r <td>IP54</td>\r <td>Spray water and dust proof &ndash; essential for construction sites</td>\r </tr>\r </tbody>\r </table>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('20081211134731', '20081020145007', '20081210181519', 'Leica Lino L2', NULL, '<strong><span class="teaser">The timeconsuming and tedious drawing of lines on the wall is a thing of the past. The Leica LINO&trade; L2 projects exactly, quickly and easily &ndash; allowing you to concentrate on the job in hand.</span></strong>\r <br /><br /><span class="text"><strong>Self-levelling</strong><br />It is not necessary to tediously align the device to obtain horizontal or vertical lines. Minor angular misalignments of &plusmn; 4&deg; are compensated automatically. If the angular misalignment is greater, the device does not project any lines. Errors are prevented.</span>\r <br /><br /><span class="text"><strong>Very easy to see laser lines</strong><br />It is possible, e.g., to transfer reference points from one wall to the next. Leave your spirit level and string in your tool box.</span>\r <br /><br /><span class="text"><strong>Exact 90&deg; angle</strong><br />Alignment work, such as marking 90&deg; angles, is performed at the touch of a button. You really save time!</span>\r <br /><br /><span class="text"><strong>Lock function<br /></strong>You can manually switch off the self-levelling using the lock function. The laser line can then be projected at any angle.</span>', '20081211134731-Leica-Lino-L2x.jpg', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
