('20081223175426', '20081020144855', '20080920095851', 'Bombard Typhoon 380 Inflatable', NULL, 'Fashioned by fifty years of continual technological progress,                    the Classic stays true to the traditional strengths of the original                    Zodiac&reg; - security, stability, durability - but is faster                    and has a larger cockpit space. It benefits from many developments:                    choice of 3 floors, bow bag, semi-recessed valves, optional                    adjustable wooden seat&hellip;Folded in its carrying bags, the                    Classic follows you wherever you go, fitting easily in the trunk                    or on the roof of your car. Reassuring and easy to manoeuvre,                    the Classic opens up the pleasures of boating in the easiest                    possible way.', '20081223175426-bombard_inflatablex.gif', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('20081226130253', '20081216185828', '20081216191429', 'ATN NVGB-5', NULL, 'The NVGB-5 is a night vision binocular designed for designed for individual nighttime reconnaissance. Ergonomic and rugged (metal not plastic ) the NVGB-5 is an exceptonal choice for medium range night vision usage. The NVGB-5 uses an exceptional fast 5X front lens system that provides the end user with superb resolution and image clarity. Also,&nbsp; included is a built in IR for total darkness viewing with "ON" indicator light FOV. The NVGB-5 is available with several image intensifer option to meet a wide array of specification requirement', '20081226171608-atnx.jpg', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul>\r <li>Total darkness IR...............Standard</li>\r <li>Magnification......................5x</li>\r <li>Detection range..................350 m/y</li>\r <li>Recognatio range................250 m/y</li>\r <li>Lens system.......................F1:1.4, F112mm</li>\r <li>FOV...................................8 degrees</li>\r <li>Diopter adjustment..............+/-5</li>\r <li>Power supply.......................one 1.5 volt AA size</li>\r <li>Range of focus....................0.3 to ifinity</li>\r <li>Controls.............................Digital--ON/IR ON with FOV indicator/OFF</li>\r <li>Battery life..........................10-20 hours</li>\r <li>Dimensions.........................318mm X 102mm X 92mm / 12.5" X 4.0" X 3.6"</li>\r <li>Weight................................1.35kg ? 3lbs</li>\r </ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('20081226171932', '20081216185828', '20081216191429', 'ATN Night Jaguar', NULL, 'Night vision binoculars are an amazing investment for someone who loves the outdoors.&nbsp; When camping in the woods or on a game hunt, night vision binoculars allow us to see into the wilderness in a way that humanity never though possible before.&nbsp; We can now assess the situation at night, observing the undulations of the ecosystem, and figuring out our place in that wilderness at night, not as a segregated out of tune entity but as a part of the thriving animal population.\r <br /><br />&nbsp;There are animals that come out solely at night.&nbsp; They are some of the most beautiful animals in the wild and we finally have our chance at spotting them and seeing their habits first hand.', '20081226171932-night-jaguar-binocularsx.jpg', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul>\r <li>Magnification.....................4X</li>\r <li>FOV.................................12 degrees</li>\r <li>Weight.............................1.4 KG</li>\r <li>Leght...............................240MM </li>\r </ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('20081226172611', '20081216185828', '20081216191429', 'ATN Night Scout Binocular', NULL, 'If you want the best in Night vision binoculars available then look no farther than the ATN Night Scout These binoculars come with a high resolution 1st generation intensifer tube, which give you a light amplification of 35,000 max.&nbsp; The computerized proximity sensor, when activated turns the unit on when in viewing position and off when not.&nbsp; The heavy coated 90mm optics glass allow for optimum clarity and distance.&nbsp; The best part is that if thre is no light to amplify , with the help of the infrared illuminator, you can cut through even the darkest darkness.With aluminum alloy construction the ATN Night Scout is the choice for rugged reliable night vision binoculars.<br /><br />PLEASE NOTE:&nbsp; There are many variables which influence the distance one sees with night vision devices-amongst them the object&rsquo;s size, the level of detail being sought and the observation conditions.&nbsp; Night vision devices detect much further under a full moon and clear skies than they will under a new moon and cloudy skies.&nbsp; Many different formulas are used to determine the statistic of maximum viewing range and this varies by manufacturer, so ultimately the generation of the intensifier tube is much more relevant than any quoted statistic when determining the maximum viewing range.', '20081226172611-atnnightscoutnightvisionbinocular_picturex.jpg', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<blockquote>\r <br /><br /><strong>Specifications:</strong>\r <br /><br />Total darkness tech. Standard<br /> Microprocessor Phillips<br /> Magnification 5X<br /> Intensifier tube high res. 1st.GEN+<br /> Detection range 150m (250m)<br /> Recognition range 100m (175m)<br /> Light gain 35,000 max<br /> Lens system 6/9 el., 90mm,F1.2<br /> FOV 20 deg.<br /> Diopter adjustment +/- 5<br /> Resolution 40 lp/mm<br /> Power supply 2&times;3 volt lithium<br /> Range of focus 20&prime; to infinity<br /> Controls Digital<br /> Battery life 10-20 hours<br /> Dimensions 225&times;150x60 mm<br /> Weight 1.5 kg\r </blockquote>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
