('20081217175626', '20081020144855', '20080920095851', 'Bombard Commando C3 3.80 Metre Inflatable', NULL, 'The Commando is the emblematic boat of the Bombard range. It is an adventurer with a solid reputation among explorers. It has a solid and resistant aluminium floor, as well as a rigid keel which provides excellent seaworthiness.\r <br /><br />The commando range can be folded away into carry bags and is ideally suited for diving, fishing or just leisure cruising.\r <br /><br />The Commando range has a monobloc floorboard system. It is made from anodised aluminium, is rust and rot proof, handles shock with ease and has a built in track for attaching accessories and equipment.\r <br /><br />The Commando C3 comes complete with:\r <ul>\r <li>Rigid keel in 3 sections</li>\r <li>Aluminium floor boards with built in track</li>\r <li>Aluminium motor plate</li>\r <li>Attachment points for launching wheels</li>\r <li>2 self-bailers</li>\r <li>Double thread 1100 decitex fabric</li>\r <li>Semi-recessed valves</li>\r <li>Lacing cuff and safety grab line with front attachment cuff</li>\r <li>Spray deflecting large profile rubbing strake</li>\r <li>2 towing rings</li>\r <li>2 lifting rings</li>\r <li>4 carrying handles</li>\r <li>Reinforced cone ends</li>\r <li>Carry Bags</li>\r <li>Fittings for rigid foredeck</li>\r <li>Paddles</li>\r <li>Footpump</li>\r <li>Repair kit</li>\r <li>Owners manual</li>\r <li>Pressure gauge</li>\r </ul>', '20081217175626-ed_4691_commando rangex.jpg', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<table border="0">\r <tbody>\r <tr>\r <td width="49%" align="right" valign="top">\r <h2>Specification</h2>\r </td>\r <td width="51%" valign="top"></td>\r </tr>\r <tr>\r <td align="right" valign="top">Overall Length</td>\r <td align="left" valign="top">3.80m</td>\r </tr>\r <tr>\r <td align="right" valign="top">Inside Length</td>\r <td align="left" valign="top">2.50m</td>\r </tr>\r <tr>\r <td align="right" valign="top">Width Overall</td>\r <td align="left" valign="top">1.7