('20090127183203', '20081020144912', '20080920100720', 'Racor 500FG Turbine Series', NULL, 'Racor 500FG system is the Racor Turbine Series and it&#39;s fuel filter and water separator are the most reliable engine protection you can install. 2 micron filter included.', '20090127183203-racor_turbine_500FGx.jpg', 1, 0, '1550000', NULL, NULL, 'The legendary Turbine Series is a fixture whenever engines demand the confidence of heavy duty, high capacity water separation and fuel filtration.  <br /><br /><strong>500FG Features</strong>\r <ul>\r <li>See-thru bowl </li>\r <li>2 Micron filter </li>\r </ul>\r <br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />500 FG Replacement elements: 2010SMOR 2 Micron or 2010PMOR 30 Micron', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
