('20090129184355', '20081020144912', '20080920100747', 'Baystar, Hydraulic Steering Kit', NULL, 'At last the affordable Baystar Outboard Hydraulic Steering Kit has a compact cylinder requiring only 21" of splashwell width, and now fits most outboard powered pontoon boats, deckboats, fishing boats and runabouts where horspower does not exceed 150. Why fight the torque on outboard powered boats when Baystar makes steering easy and boating more enjoyable. One kit fits most applications, and includes 20&#39; of tubing that can be cut to length. Everything you need for the installation. Contains: HH4016, Helm pump, 1 ea. HC4645H, Compact style steering cylinder, 1 ea. *adapter kits for certain engines may be required, HT4420H, Steering lines, 2 ea. *each hose is 20&#39; long and the helm connection can be cut for your specific installation, HA5430, oil, 2 ea.', '20090129184355-baystar-teleflex.jpg', 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
('20090129184840', '20081020144912', '20080920100747', 'Teleflex Seastar Hydraulic Steering Kit', NULL, '<span>Full hydraulic steering kits make turning single or twin motors of up to 600 horsepower  a breeze. Can be used on larger boats and for speeds up of to 60 miles per hour,  these low-resistance hydraulic systems come as a kit with a teleflex helm, hydraulic  cylinder, fittings, hydraulic oil, a bleeder kit and instructions. <br /> <br /> <strong>Technical Information: </strong><br /> 1.7 Steering Kit (without Hoses) HK6400<br /> <br /> <strong>Components: </strong><br /> SeaStar 1.7 Helm HH5271<br /> Pivot Front Mount O/B Cylinder HC5345<br /> SeaStar Oil (1 Quart Mil Spec H5606)HA5430 (x2)<br /> <br /> Hose priced per pair.<br /> <em>Use of nylon tubing is not recommended for SeaStar outboard steering. </em></span>', '20090129184840-telefle-sea-starx.jpg', 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
